[{"id":6767566938,"node_id":"REFE_lADOAQ-n5M5LJ90DzwAAAAGTYOBa","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/rclone/rclone/issues/events/6767566938","actor":{"login":"ncw","id":536803,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjUzNjgwMw==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/536803?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw","html_url":"https://github.com/ncw","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"event":"referenced","commit_id":"e9c5a27da05aec6a17cf704c12e3ac547cf1f706","commit_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/rclone/rclone/commits/e9c5a27da05aec6a17cf704c12e3ac547cf1f706","created_at":"2022-06-08T08:11:20Z","performed_via_github_app":null},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/rclone/rclone/issues/comments/1149602110","html_url":"https://github.com/rclone/rclone/issues/6217#issuecomment-1149602110","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/rclone/rclone/issues/6217","id":1149602110,"node_id":"IC_kwDOAQ-n5M5EhYk-","user":{"login":"ncw","id":536803,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjUzNjgwMw==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/536803?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw","html_url":"https://github.com/ncw","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2022-06-08T08:11:59Z","updated_at":"2022-06-08T08:11:59Z","body":"Rclone doesn't log the error because it passes it on to the upper layers. Unfortunately exactly what the error is gets lost in translation and appears as `Input/output error (5)` to the user.\r\n\r\nThe layers involved are\r\n\r\n1. drive backend\r\n2. vfs\r\n3. rclone mount\r\n4. fuse\r\n5. kernel\r\n6. user application\r\n\r\nUnfortunately fuse can only take a small number of numeric error messages so going between 3 -> 4 the error is translated and the context is lost.\r\n\r\nHere is the function which does that\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/rclone/rclone/blob/e11bfacfcf42e528942246c7248d2412f9d3977a/cmd/mount/fs.go#L75-L106\r\n\r\nSo perhaps what rclone should be doing is in the case that there isn't an exact match for the error it should be logging the error at ERROR level - that would make it visible to the user.  `translateError` would need a bit more context to make the error message useful - it would need the path in use, but I think that would satisfy your requirements.\r\n\r\nWhat do you think?\r\n\r\nWe do in fact do this already in the Windows/macOS mounting code\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/rclone/rclone/blob/e11bfacfcf42e528942246c7248d2412f9d3977a/cmd/cmount/fs.go#L596\r\n\r\nI've had a go at this - can you give it a test?\r\n\r\n[v1.59.0-beta.6172.e9c5a27da.fix-6217-mount-errors](https://beta.rclone.org/branch/fix-6217-mount-errors/v1.59.0-beta.6172.e9c5a27da.fix-6217-mount-errors/) on branch [fix-6217-mount-errors](https://github.com/rclone/rclone/tree/fix-6217-mount-errors) (uploaded in 15-30 mins)\r\n\r\n","author_association":"MEMBER","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/rclone/rclone/issues/comments/1149602110/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null,"event":"commented","actor":{"login":"ncw","id":536803,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjUzNjgwMw==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/536803?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw","html_url":"https://github.com/ncw","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false}},{"id":6767573454,"node_id":"LE_lADOAQ-n5M5LJ90DzwAAAAGTYPnO","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/rclone/rclone/issues/events/6767573454","actor":{"login":"ncw","id":536803,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjUzNjgwMw==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/536803?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw","html_url":"https://github.com/ncw","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.gith